'''Gisimenti''' ni ahantu hazwi cyane mu mujyi wa Kigali. Hazwi kw'izina rya [[Kigali]] Car Free Zone.
Gisimenti iherereye mu murenge wa Remera, hafi ya [[Stade Amahoro]] aha hantu uhasanga ibikorwa byu bucuruzi byinshi,  nki cyicaro gikuru cya Airtel mu [[Rwanda]],Lando hoteri, Banki ya Kigali,Zigama Bank, ishami rya MTN.
Gisimenti abantu bahurira hamwe bagamije kwishimisha bagendeye kubyo bakunda. Gisimenti yamenyekane cyane kubikorwa bihakorerwa mu masaha ya nijoro.
Ibyabereye Gisimenti mu masaha ya nijoro byagiye bivugwa cyane
mubinyamakuru byandika no ku mbuga nkoranyambaga.

